  "body": "<p style=\"margin: 0px;\"></p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px;font-size: 20px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom:10px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Trebuchet MS; color: #222;\">Art, Science, and Love\n</h3>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px 0px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0px;text-align: left; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Trebuchet MS; margin: 0px;\">You’ve dedicated yourself to achieving your goals and worked hard throughout your career. You recognize and deserve the very best. Viewing fine art in your home or office, decreases stress levels, increases empathy, raises critical thinking skills, and helps provide relief from mental exhaustion.  One study conducted by a neurobiologist found that your brain releases dopamine, the chemical of pleasure, when viewing fine art.  Just like each fine art painting is a one-of-a-kind original, so are you.  The bottom-line, is that you are the best expert on what you love.  Trust your instincts, trust yourself.\n</p>\n\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"><!--[if mso]>\n  <v:roundrect xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" href=\"http://\" style=\"height:40px;v-text-anchor:middle;width:300px;\" arcsize=\"10%\" stroke=\"f\" fillcolor=\"#222222\">\n    <w:anchorlock/>\n    <center>\n  <![endif]-->\n      <a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/Artists--Bios.html\" style=\"background-color:#222222;border-radius:4px;color:#ffffff;display:inline-block;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;line-height:40px;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;width:300px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;\">Come see what you love</a>\n  <!--[if mso]>\n    </center>\n  </v:roundrect>\n<![endif]--></div>\n\n\n\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/Middle-Banner.jpg\" alt=\"Spotlight on Art\n\" style=\"width: 100%; height:auto; max-width:660px; margin:auto; display:block;\"></p>\n\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px;font-size: 20px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-top: 20px; padding-bottom:10px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px; font-weight: bold; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Trebuchet MS; color: #222;\">Talented artists that stand the test of time</h3>\n<p style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px 0px;line-height: 24px;margin: 0px;text-align: left; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, Verdana, Trebuchet MS;\">No doubt you’ve seen the articles where so-called modern abstract art has sold for millions of dollars.  Most Modern abstract art is a commercial fad, built more upon the artists brand than true talent.  When all our customers fall in love with a painting and proudly hang it on their wall, they do not need to try to explain what it is that is being viewed.  Everyone intuitively knows that it is the work of a very talented artist and that both you and the artist, with whom you bonded, in spirit, know the value of your unique treasure – the perfect composition that captures true beauty.</p>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/john_adams_parker_adirondacks.html\"><img style=\"width: 94%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/john_adams_parker_grid.jpg\" width=\"615\" height=\"340\" alt=\"Robert Decker - A Fall Landscape\n\"></a></td>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/william_sidney_cooper_landscape.html\"><img style=\"width: 94%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/sidney_cooper_grid.jpg\" width=\"589\" height=\"390\" alt=\"Charles Augustus Lasar - Sunset \n\"></a></td>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/edward_moran_breakers.html\"><img style=\"width: 92%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/edward_moran_grid.jpg\" width=\"717\" height=\"449\" alt=\"Barton Stone Hays - Still Life with Peaches, Grapes, and Lemonade\n\"></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr><td colspan=\"3\"><div style=\"padding-top: 10px;\">&nbsp;</div></td></tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/barton_stone_hays_tabletop.html\"><img style=\"width: 94%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/barton_stone_hays_artwork_grid.jpg\" width=\"639\" height=\"467\" alt=\"Felix Octavius Darley - Washington and Companions \n\"></a></td>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/penrhyn_stanlaws_lincoln.html\"><img style=\"width: 80%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/stanlaws_grid.jpg\" width=\"403\" height=\"489\" alt=\"Max Weyl - Rock Creek Park \n\"></a></td>\n      <td width=\"30%\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/etienn_adolphe_piot_note.html\"><img style=\"width: 80%; height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.bedfordfineartgallery.com/mailers/img/IMG_4382_grid.jpg\" width=\"449\" height=\"540\" alt=\"Charles Wilson Knapp - Pastoral Landscape \n\"></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"
